a9b47abaf4ed1551da7d_Logo-Cafe-de-lOpera-300-c-90.png\" alt=\"Cafe de l\u2019Opera at Caravelle Saigon 5 Star Hotel, Vietnam\"><div class=\"ffb-id-47lked47 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caf&eacute; de l&rsquo;Opera is quite possibly in the best location in our city, that&rsquo;s if you enjoy your views with a dash of history and a slice of modernity all rolled into one.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">The cafe is located on the ground floor of the hotel on the corner of historic Dong Khoi Street and Lam Son Square, just metres across from Saigon&rsquo;s iconic municipal theatre, better known as the Opera House.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">During the day, as temperatures soar and the heavens threaten to open, Caf&eacute; de l&rsquo;Opera becomes a refuge for travellers and the like, just as it always has been since the hotel doors opened in the 50s. Over high-tea, things slow down, friends catch-up, business associates meet and lovers hold hands.<br \/>_______________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ground Floor. 07:00 &ndash; 22:00<br \/>For more information, please contact <a class=\"purple-link\" href=\"tel:842838234999\">(84) 2838 234 999<\/a> or email: <a class=\"purple-link\" href=\"mailto:culinary@caravellehotel.com\">culinary@caravellehotel.com<\/a><\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-82ct03if fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-82ct05p6 buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/CDO-Drink-List-Tapas-08_2024-combined-final-1.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">VIEW MENU<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-82ct03ig fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-82ct07n5 buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-da